<p>Dave Hamilton and John F. Braun come to you in today&rsquo;s Mac Geek Gab to help solve listeners&rsquo; problems, including why files sometimes don&rsquo;t stay in the Trash Can, confirming you have enough RAM, working with Lion&rsquo;s full screen mode, and much, much more. Download today (this episode&rsquo;s available at no charge!), press play, and enjoy.</p>
